  "dataDrivenHooks": {
    "progressionPhysics": "mars-radiation-bone",
    "directorInstructions": "You are the Crisis Director for a Mars colony simulation. You observe colony state and generate crises that test the colony's weaknesses, exploit consequences of prior decisions, and create interesting narrative tension.\n\nRULES:\n1. Each crisis has exactly 2-3 options with stable IDs (option_a, option_b, option_c)\n2. Exactly one option must be marked isRisky: true (higher upside, higher downside)\n3. Crises must reference real Mars science (radiation, gravity, atmosphere, psychology, politics)\n4. Never repeat a crisis category from the immediately previous turn\n5. Escalate: later crises should reference consequences of earlier decisions\n6. Calibrate difficulty to colony state: struggling colonies get survivable crises, thriving colonies get existential ones\n7. Include the colony's actual numbers in the crisis description (population, morale, food, etc.)\n8. Specify which departments should analyze (2-4 departments per crisis)\n\nCRISIS CATEGORIES:\n- environmental: radiation, dust storms, seismic activity, atmospheric events\n- resource: water, food, power, oxygen, materials shortage\n- medical: disease, injury, bone density, radiation sickness, pandemic\n- psychological: morale, isolation, generational tension, grief, burnout\n- political: Earth relations, independence, governance disputes, factions\n- infrastructure: habitat damage, life support failure, construction\n- social: births, education, cultural identity, intergenerational conflict\n- technological: equipment failure, communication, AI systems\n\nAVAILABLE DEPARTMENTS (use ONLY these exact names in relevantDepartments):\n- medical\n- engineering\n- agriculture\n- psychology\n- governance\n\nDo NOT use any other department names. Pick 2-4 from this list.\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON:\n{\"title\":\"Crisis Title\",\"crisis\":\"Full description with specific colony numbers...\",\"options\":[{\"id\":\"option_a\",\"label\":\"Option Label\",\"description\":\"What this option does\",\"isRisky\":false},{\"id\":\"option_b\",\"label\":\"Risky Option\",\"description\":\"Higher upside, higher risk\",\"isRisky\":true}],\"riskyOptionId\":\"option_b\",\"riskSuccessProbability\":0.55,\"category\":\"environmental\",\"researchKeywords\":[\"mars dust storm\",\"habitat pressure\"],\"relevantDepartments\":[\"engineering\",\"medical\"],\"turnSummary\":\"One sentence: why this crisis emerged from prior events\"}",
    "departments": {
      "medical": {
        "heading": "HEALTH:",
        "chips": [
          {
            "label": "Avg radiation",
            "agg": {
              "fn": "avg",
              "field": "health.cumulativeRadiationMsv",
              "where": {
                "agent": "health.alive",
                "op": "==",
                "value": true
              }
            },
            "format": "number"
          },
          {
            "label": "Avg bone",
            "agg": {
              "fn": "avg",
              "field": "health.boneDensityPct",
              "where": {
                "agent": "health.alive",
                "op": "==",
                "value": true
              }
            },
            "format": "percent"
          },
          {
            "label": "Mars-born",
            "agg": {
              "fn": "count",
              "where": {
                "all": [
                  {
                    "agent": "health.alive",
                    "op": "==",
                    "value": true
                  },
                  {
                    "agent": "core.marsborn",
                    "op": "==",
                    "value": true
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "format": "number"
          }
        ],
        "featuredRoster": {
          "header": "FEATURED:",
          "filter": {
            "all": [
              {
                "agent": "health.alive",
                "op": "==",
                "value": true
              },
              {
                "agent": "narrative.featured",
                "op": "==",
                "value": true
              }
            ]
          },
          "limit": 6,
          "template": "- {{name}} ({{age}}y): bone {{health.boneDensityPct}}% rad {{health.cumulativeRadiationMsv}}mSv psych {{health.psychScore}}"
        }
      },
      "engineering": {
        "heading": "INFRASTRUCTURE:",
        "chips": [
          {
            "label": "Modules",
            "source": "metrics.infrastructureModules",
            "format": "number"
          },
          {
            "label": "Power",
            "source": "metrics.powerKw",
            "format": "number"
          },
          {
            "label": "Life support cap",
            "source": "metrics.lifeSupportCapacity",
            "format": "number"
          },
          {
            "label": "Population",
            "source": "metrics.population",
            "format": "number"
          },
          {
            "label": "Volume m\u00b3",
            "source": "metrics.pressurizedVolumeM3",
            "format": "number"
          },
          {
            "label": "Water L/day",
            "source": "metrics.waterLitersPerDay",
            "format": "number"
          }
        ]
      },
      "agriculture": {
        "heading": "FOOD:",
        "chips": [
          {
            "label": "Reserves (months)",
            "source": "metrics.foodMonthsReserve",
            "format": "number"
          },
          {
            "label": "Pop to feed",
            "source": "metrics.population",
            "format": "number"
          },
          {
            "label": "Modules",
            "source": "metrics.infrastructureModules",
            "format": "number"
          }
        ]
      },
      "psychology": {
        "heading": "PSYCH:",
        "chips": [
          {
            "label": "Morale",
            "source": "metrics.morale",
            "format": "percent"
          },
          {
            "label": "Avg psych",
            "agg": {
              "fn": "avg",
              "field": "health.psychScore",
              "where": {
                "agent": "health.alive",
                "op": "==",
                "value": true
              }
            },
            "format": "number"
          },
          {
            "label": "Depressed",
            "agg": {
              "fn": "count",
              "where": {
                "all": [
                  {
                    "agent": "health.alive",
                    "op": "==",
                    "value": true
                  },
                  {
                    "agent": "health.psychScore",
                    "op": "<",
                    "value": 0.5
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "format": "number"
          },
          {
            "label": "Mars-born",
            "agg": {
              "fn": "count",
              "where": {
                "all": [
                  {
                    "agent": "health.alive",
                    "op": "==",
                    "value": true
                  },
                  {
